de.oaam.model.oaam.capabilities

Interface CapabilitiesContainerA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Capabilities, Subcapabilities
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CapabilitiesContainerAImpl, CapabilitiesImpl, SubcapabilitiesImpl

    public interface CapabilitiesContainerA
extends OaamBaseElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Container A'. The root of the capabilities mode.

    The following features are supported:

    • Task On Device Capabilities
    • Signal On Connection Or Device Capabilities
    • Device In Location Capabilities
    • Subdevice In Device Capabilities
    • Connection In Duct Or Location Capabilities
    • Subcapabilities
    • Subconnection In Device Capabilities
    See Also:
    CapabilitiesPackage.getCapabilitiesContainerA()
